page.title: 17Biggin Dale.
page.content: A{National Nature Reserve}has been established in{Biggin Dale. Among the{flowers}we found in this Reserve are :_ Wild Purple Orchid, Cowslip,Buttercups,Celandine, Daisy,Dandelion,Forget_me_nots, Speedwels,Wild Strawberrys, Lords and Ladies,Butter Burn,Crane's Bill. In our visit we also saw :_ Brimstone Butterflies,Orange Tip Butterflies,Cabbage White and many hairy caterpillars.We saw a red spider The{birds}we saw in the area include:_ Willow Warble,Cuckoo, Dippers,Pigeon, Wheatear _ which is unusual for this area. Robin and an Owl.
